```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "resource_manager": "Slurm",
    "partition": "# set partition name",
    "node": "# set node name",
    "gpus": "# set number of GPUs",
    "cpus_per_gpu": "# set number of CPUs per GPU",
    "memory": "1",
    "job_name": "multi-gpu-training",
    "output_file": "logs/multi-gpu-training_%A_%a.out",
    "error_file": "logs/multi-gpu-training_%A_%a.err",
    "account": "# set account name",
    "array_job": "0-15%1",
    "container_runtime": "Singularity",
    "container_image": "image",
    "container_volume": "/myovision:/mnt",
    "container_command": "cd /mnt/myovision-sam && torchrun --standalone --nproc_per_node=gpu train.py",
    "framework": "PyTorch",
    "training_script": "train.py"
  }
}
```
